        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <dt class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </dt>
          <dd>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Centralisation</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Une source unique de vérité pour toutes les parties prenantes</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <dt class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </dt>
          <dd>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Spécialisation</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Des outils conçus spécifiquement pour le monde du jeu de société</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <dt class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-sky-100 rounded-xl mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </dt>
          <dd>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Capitalisation</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Transformer les données de chaque édition en savoir réutilisable</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

